      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink-500">Model-agnostic by design: fully-Swiss Apertus by default, or a European (Mistral) or international (Llama, Qwen) open-weight base where your compliance allows — whichever wins your evaluation, all running on your own infrastructure. See the <a class="link-underline" href="/concepts/small-models/">base-model spectrum</a>.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-500">Want the depth behind each layer? The <a class="link-underline" href="/concepts/">concepts pages</a> cover small models, quantization, evaluation and the sovereign runtime in detail.</p>
