  <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-sm text-ink-500">Every engagement ships with the evaluation report; the full compliance &amp; audit pack — model card, training-data lineage record, DPA template, TOMs, EU AI Act risk-classification worksheet — is scoped where your obligations require it. This is not legal advice — we work with your compliance and legal teams to meet your obligations.</p>
</section>

